    "title": "Real-world probability",
    "prompt": "In a population of grasshoppers, the ratio of grasshoppers with a white marking to<br>\r\nthose without a white marking is 2:3. An entomologist captures and photographs <br>\r\n290 grasshoppers. How many photographs are likely to show grasshoppers with <br>\r\na white marking?<\/br>",
